Configure FHIR Store Search<pre><code>search_config = {
    "searchParameters": [
        {
            "name": "patient-name",
            "definition": "Patient.name",
            "type": "string"
        }
    ]
} # (1)!

search_config = healthcare.configure_search( # (2)!
    config=search_config,
    store_name="my-store",
    dataset_name="my-dataset",
    validate_only=False,  # (3)!
    project_id="my-project",  # (4)!
    location="us-central1",  # (5)!
)
print(f"Search configuration: {search_config}")
</code></pre> <ol> <li>Define the search configuration</li> <li>Configure search parameters for a FHIR store</li> <li>Optional: if True, validates the configuration without applying it</li> <li>Optional: defaults to the project associated with credentials</li> <li>Optional: defaults to the default location</li> </ol>
